      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i live in oslo and since its winter and basically no sun i've been feeling really low on energy. i read online that taking a super high dose of vitamin d can fix that quickly. is it safe if i take like 50,000 iu a day for a few weeks just to really boost my levels up and get my immunity back? i dont want to go to the doctors for a blood test if i dont have to",
