      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've seen a lot of biohacking forums saying that loading up on high doses for a short burst is the only way to actually see a difference in blood levels. if i just do it for two weeks and then stop, wouldn't that be fine? i'm pretty healthy otherwise and dont really have the time for doctor appointments right now.",
